name: G.O.A.T.
description: G.O.A.T. is a hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Animal Pie and ACDC. This strain provides effects that are ideal for treating general pain and anxiety. G.O.A.T. features a flavor profile that is bursting with fragrant cherry aromas. With a 1:1 ratio of CBD and THC, this strain is preferred by patients treating chronic pain, multiple sclerosis, and cancer.
